And having thrown it together so many times after a long day, now i know why mom made it so often - it’s easy, inexpensive and ALWAYS delicious. My version deepens flavor with white wine and has frozen lobster I found in the freezer. Recipe on fitmencook.com. Can you dig it? Boom. (traducción abajo)

Comía este plato mucho cuando era niño - camarones y maíz al estilo Cajun.  Es muy sencillo, barato y no requiere muchos ingredientes  Y CLARO ES MUY RICO! Mi versión usa vino blanco y también tiene langosta que encontré en el congelador. Receta en fitmencook.com. Lo comerías?! Bum.

We have a goal to raise $3.5 million – that’s up to 35 million meals for kids across the country who are not getting the food they need. 

Also, if you VOTE FOR MY DESIGN (link in bio), the designer with the most votes will have an additional $5,000 donated to @nokidhungry in their name on behalf of @williamssonoma!

node.text:
Salute 🙌🏾 to all the fathers holding it down in the kitchen. Huge thanks to everyone who sent pics and videos and stories -  it was definitely inspiring to see and read the impact men make when they cook for their families. Couldn’t get to every story and pic but THANK YOU ALL for sending! Happy Father’s Day to all the fathers and fatherly figures in our lives - keep cheffing it up! Boom.
—
Aquí hay un poco de motivación para cocinar con tu familia! Un brindis a todos los hombres preparando platos muy ricos en la cocina. Muchas gracias a todos los que nos enviaron fotos, vídeos y unos cuentos - sin duda inspiraron darnos cuenta del impacto en el hogar cuando los hombres cocinan para la familia. No podría incluir todas las foto que nos enviaron, pero ¡GRACIAS por enviar! Feliz #DíadelosPadres a todos los hombres y figuras paternas de nuestras vidas - ¡sigo cocinando! Boom.

🔥 Can you dig it? if you’ve wondered how I come up with new recipes, it’s by taking recipes I love then recreating them in new, healthful ways for ME. If you wanna try this shrimp Alfredo, go to fitmencook.com for the full recipe and nutritional breakdown. Comment below what food we should deconstruct and reimagine next! Boom. (traducción abajo)
—
😱 Pasta Alfredo con camarones, solo 600 calorías!🙌🏾. Lo comerías?  Si te has preguntado cómo se me ocurren las recetas que cocino, es por transformar las recetas que me encantan comer y luego recrearlas de formas nuevas y saludables para MÍ. Si quieres probar este plato, echa vistazo a fitmencook.com para conseguir la receta completa y los datos nutricionales. ¡Comenta a continuación qué comida deberíamos deconstruir y reinventar para el pròximo video! Bum.

There’s no 100% perfect response because we are all different; but, if we just lead with empathy and compassion, we can better understand each other and people can get the help they need. If you feel comfortable, please comment below some of the helpful and healthful ways people have encouraged you to be mentally strong. Boom.

😱 These arayes (or grilled burgers in a pita 😅) were AMAZING! I saw these on @bengingi and had to try! Less than 300 calories for 2 of these with over 30g protein, 38g carbs and 3g fat! These are a VERY popular Middle Eastern cuisine with many believing they originated in Lebanon 🇱🇧. It’d be easy to swap in veggie ground or other lean meats like turkey, and change the flavor with some new seasonings! I especially love these for portion control, for kids AND for parties or tailgates. So, can you dig it?! Tag someone who would love these! Boom. (Traduccion abajo)
—
😱 ¡Estos arayes (o hamburguesas a la parrilla en una pita 😅) eran INCREÍBLES! ¡Los vi en pagina de @bengingi y tuve que intentarlo! ¡Menos de 300 calorías para 2 con más de 30g de proteína, 38g de carbohidratos y 3g de grasa! Se trata de una cocina de Oriente Medio MUY popular y muchos creen que se originaron en el Líbano 🇱🇧. ¡Sería sencillo cambiar entre carne molida a base de plantas u otras carnes magras como el pavo, y cambiar el sabor con algunos condimentos nuevos! Me encantan especialmente estos para practicar el control de porciones, para los niños Y para fiestas. Entonces, ¿lo comerías? ¡Etiqueta a un amigo quien le encantarían estos! Bum.

Can you dig it - a smoked veggie grain bowl?! Smoking veggies #onthegrill makes even picky eaters enjoy them, including kids! (almost like dumping cheese on them - I know I’m not the only who ate that as a child 😅) Grab this recipe from @williamssonoma and be on the lookout for more of my smoked recipes on the @traegergrills. And to address a FAQ, if you’re looking for a good, non-intimidating grill,  I always recommend #traeger - every friend I’ve convinced to get one loves it. Easy to use with the wood pellets and heat control is just like using an oven 👍🏾, just with smoke. I smoked my chili (with no beans 😒) for a few hours and it was some of the best I ever had. Comment below if you have one, or thinking of getting one, to let people know they’re legit!  And check out my recipe as well - you’ll love it. Boom. (traducción abajo)
—
¿Lo comerías - un tazón de granos y verduras ahumado?  Ahumar las verduras hace que incluso los más quisquillosos las disfruten, ¡incluso los niños!  Consigue esta receta de @williamssonoma y esté atento a más de mis recetas ahumadas en @traegergrills.  Y para responder a las preguntas frecuentes, si estás buscando una buena parrilla que no te intimide, siempre recomiendo #traeger: a todos los amigos que he convencido de conseguir una le encanta!  Fácil de usar con los pellets de madera y el control del calor es como usar un horno 👍🏾, solo con humo.  Ahumé mi chile con carne (sin frijoles 😒) durante unas horas y fue uno de las mejores versiones que he probado.  Comenta a continuación si tienes un #traeger (o estás pensando en comprar una) para que la gente sepa que es legítimo y mira mi receta también, te encantará.  Bum.

Pasta game 💪🏾 for #lunch, dinner or your next cookout! Many of us have a favorite pasta salad recipe using mayonnaise. But this salmon pasta salad that replaces mayo with tahini & reduced fat parmesan is 🔥!! I had something similar at a restaurant recently and had to try it myself. Perfect for the cookout and summer/fall parties! Comment below if you want this uploaded to fitmencook.com and I’ll get it loaded tonight! 🙌🏾Boom. (Traduccion abajo)
—
¡Pasta 💪🏾 para #Almuerzo, #cena o fiesta! Ok, sé que la mayoría de nosotros tenemos una receta favorita de ensalada de pasta con mayonesa. ¡Pero esta ensalada de pasta con salmón que reemplaza la mayonesa con tahini (pasta de sésamo) y queso parmesano reducido en grasa es puro🔥! ¡Perfecto para las fiestas de verano/otoño! ¡Comenta a continuación si quieres que esta receta se cargue en fitmencook.com y lo publicaré esta noche! Bum.

Weekend photo dump. Got to spend quality with all 4 of my nephews and this time no cutting boards were split in half! 😅 Just video games + a $30 Disney movie 🤯😑 (is that what parents are paying now?!) + donuts + lots of noise and laughter. 😎👍🏾 And now my oldest  nephew wears the same shoe size?! 😭  It’s weird - I feel exhausted but also energized for the week! Boom. (traducción abajo)
—
Fotos del finde. Tenía la oportunidad pasar tiempo con mis sobrinos y esta vez ellos no rompieron mi nueva tabla de cortar. 😅 Solo juegos de video + una película de Disney que costó $30 🤯😑 + donuts +mucho ruido y risa! Es increíble que me siento agotado pero también energizado! Bum.

node.text:
How it started vs. How it’s going…Most people don’t know but I used an antique sewing desk I found at a thrift store to film recipes in 2015. The machine was always out of view so you never saw it. 😄 I put it by the window b/c it had the best light and everyone always asked what type of studio lighting I had. (the sun ☀️)

When I moved to a studio b/c my condo was overrun by kitchen gadgets, it was a relief and a moment of panic because I had to figure out which dream to pursue first. I’ll admit this now but I put a lot of my dreams on hold “waiting” to be picked and building others’ dreams. The stuff behind the scenes often made it difficult to genuinely smile and love what I do - I was locked into contracts for deals only to have them given to someone else that fit the look they wanted but with my ideas. I’m NOT special - this happens all the time so I’m not feeling sorry for myself.  I’m just giving context for WHY my smile today is big. 😊

Today, I started building one of those dreams…nearly 7 years after filming content by the window on a sewing desk, we wrapped filming for our first master-class series. 🙌🏾 The first of what I hope is a library of content to help us live healthier and happier - mentally, physically & spiritually. 💯 I’m no longer waiting, I’m building. 💪🏾 THANKS for sticking with me all these years! It’s going to be an incredible ride!! Who’s ready for this content?! Boom. (traducción en @fitmencookespanol )
